34:30.636 --> 34:33.305
- That's so sad.

34:33.339 --> 34:38.477
Nobody to buy you presents
just for the hell of it.

34:38.510 --> 34:40.412
- Like your dad

34:40.446 --> 34:42.814
brought you when he came back
from his college reunion.

34:42.848 --> 34:44.850
- Yeah.

34:44.883 --> 34:48.220
- He brought you
the mascot doll.

34:48.254 --> 34:51.190
And Leah got the sweatshirt.
That's...

34:51.223 --> 34:54.360
