39:42.948 --> 39:46.418
and it wasn't fair.

39:46.452 --> 39:49.120
- Why wouldn't he pick me?

39:49.154 --> 39:52.591
- You're lucky, Laurel.

39:52.624 --> 39:54.192
You're lucky

39:54.225 --> 39:56.928
that he didn't pick you.

39:56.962 --> 39:58.730
When you're running
in Central Park,

39:58.764 --> 40:01.833
you ever notice kids
throwing a rock into the pond

40:01.867 --> 40:03.602
and it makes the ripples?

40:03.635 --> 40:07.673
They grow bigger
and bigger and bigger.

40:07.706 --> 40:10.041
Destroying everything
in its wake.

40:10.075 --> 40:11.777
That's what your father did.

40:11.810 --> 40:15.681
He threw an insidious rock

40:15.714 --> 40:18.216
into your family

40:18.249 --> 40:23.121
and it covered all of you.
You, Leah.

40:23.154 --> 40:26.191
- [quietly] Uh-uh.
[sniffling]

40:26.224 --> 40:30.028
- Your father was a monster.

40:30.061 --> 40:34.633
*

40:34.666 --> 40:37.836
And the three of you are
collateral damage.

40:37.869 --> 40:40.038
- Like you.

40:40.071 --> 40:43.509
- Yeah, like me.

40:43.542 --> 40:50.816
