41:20.145 --> 41:21.680
- Damn.

41:21.713 --> 41:23.915
- Do it.

41:29.320 --> 41:32.858
- I just wanted him
to love me....

41:32.891 --> 41:35.293
Daddy.

41:35.326 --> 41:37.896
Why wouldn't he?

41:37.929 --> 41:41.199
